com.diffplug.common.swt.os

Class SwtPlatform

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diffplug.common.swt.os.SwtPlatform

  • public class SwtPlatform
extends Object
    Models the platforms that SWT binaries are built for, useful for build tools that interact with SWT jars.
